<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Leave Request</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .body {
      padding: 40px;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .body h2 {
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .box p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .box strong {
      color: #111827;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 25px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .footer p {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>HRM System</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>New Leave Request Submitted</h2>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>A new leave request has been submitted by <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong> and requires your review.</p>

      <div class="box">
        <p><strong>Employee:</strong> {{employeeName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Leave Type:</strong> {{leaveType}}</p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{startDate}} &mdash; {{endDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Please log in to the <a href="https://hrm.jevxo.com/leave"
          style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">admin dashboard</a> to approve or reject this
        request.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} HRM System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>